---
By: Eknath Easwaran
Locus:
  Page: 420
  Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Self
---
The man or woman who realizes God has everything and lacks nothing. Having
this, one desires nothing further; he cannot be shaken by the heaviest
burden of sorrow. Life cannot threaten such a person; all it holds is the
opportunity to love, to serve, and to give.
